No. 323,

Misc.

Williams v. Florida. Richard Kanner for petitioner. Earl Fair cloth, Attorney General of Florida, and Jesse J. McCrary, Jr., Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

Dist. Ct. App. Fla., 3d Dist. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Certiorari granted and case transferred to appellate docket.
